set_fall_damage

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_fall_damage -  Set the amount of damage the player will take if they fall off this roof.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_fall_damage(string type,
int damage)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - The type of fall (weak, slope, step or jump; all to set all damages the same)
%^BOLD%^damage%^RESET%^ - The amount of damage.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/rooftop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Set the amount of damage the player will take if they fall off this
roof.  This amount is somewhat randomised.

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_slope, set_jump, set_weak_roof

.EP

